; Coverage for amount.cc
; The --decimal-comma flag sets commodity_t::decimal_comma_by_default,
; which causes all output to use comma as decimal separator and period
; as thousands separator, even for $ amounts.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $12.345,67
    Assets:Cash

test bal --decimal-comma
         $-12.345,67  Assets:Cash
          $12.345,67  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
